# Computer Vision Homework 1
BLG 453E - Computer Vision - Fall 25/26

## Overview
This repository contains solutions for Homework 1, covering:
- Q1: PDF calculations (theoretical)
- Q2: Gamma correction for image enhancement
- Q3: Color segmentation using HSV
- Q4: Channel remapping to reveal hidden images

## Setup

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.11 or higher
- pip package manager

### Installation
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Usage

### Q2: Gamma Correction
```bash
cd Q2_gamma_correction
py -3.11 gamma_correction.py
```

### Q3: Color Segmentation
```bash
cd Q3_color_segmentation
py -3.11 color_segmentation.py
```

### Q4: Channel Remapping
```bash
cd Q4_channel_remapping
py -3.11 channel_remapping.py
```

## Results
All output images will be saved in the `outputs/` directory.

